    "These data were subsequently analyzed using a neural network to decipher user behavior.",
    "Table 7 Brief summary of some of the most important studies carried out in the field of medicine and biology using eye tracking and VR",
    "Example studies Brief description Melendrez-Ruiz et al. (2021) concluded that pulses were not effective eye-catchers in a VR supermarket setting after considering metrics like dwell-time and fixations count.",
